# No-Torsion root no longer deploys its own Worker backend, so the current frontend-only project does not read `.dev.vars`.
#
# Use `.env` for frontend and build-time variables instead:
# - `VITE_NCT_API_SQL_PUBLIC_DATA_URL`
# - `VITE_NCT_SUB_FORM_URL`
#
# Put Worker runtime variables in the sibling backend projects:
# - `../nct-api-sql/.dev.vars`
# - `../nct-api-sql-sub/.dev.vars`
#
# If you need the old Express / Workers stack, use `../NCT_old` rather than this root project.
